              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The proton detector was a scintillation",
                "spectrometer, consisting of a thin CsI(Tl) crystal",
                "and FEU-15B photomultiplier. The absolute value of",
                "the differential cross section of inelastic",
                "scattering was determined under the assumption that",
                "pure Coulomb scattering takes place for elastic",
                "scattering in the angle region on the order of 20",
                "degrees."
